---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Explore Singapore"
  description="Privacy Policy for Explore Singapore. Learn how we handle your data, what we collect, and how we protect your privacy."
>
  <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-[#f0f0f0]">
    <div class="max-w-[1120px] mx-auto px-6 h-[64px] flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-md bg-[#EF3340] flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="white"><path d="M128,16a88.1,88.1,0,0,0-88,88c0,75.3,80,132.17,83.36,134.55a8,8,0,0,0,9.28,0C136,236.17,216,179.3,216,104A88.1,88.1,0,0,0,128,16Zm0,56a32,32,0,1,1-32,32A32,32,0,0,1,128,72Z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a]">Explore <span class="text-[#EF3340]">Singapore</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="text-[13px] text-[#888] hover:text-[#1a1a1a] transition-colors">Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-[28px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-[14px] text-[#888] mb-10">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">What We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Explore Singapore is designed with privacy in mind. We do not require you to create an account, provide an email address, or share any personal information to use our service.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        The only data stored is kept locally in your browser via <strong>Local Storage</strong>. This includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li>Your saved itineraries and trip plans</li>
        <li>Places you have bookmarked or added to your planner</li>
        <li>Your preference settings (e.g., theme, display options)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        This data never leaves your device unless you explicitly choose to export or share it. We do not transmit, sell, or share your locally stored data with any third party.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Analytics</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand general usage patterns, such as which pages are visited and how the application is used. These analytics do not collect personally identifiable information and do not use cookies for tracking purposes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        We do not build user profiles, track you across websites, or sell data to advertisers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Explore Singapore does not set any tracking cookies. We may use essential cookies strictly necessary for the functioning of the service (such as remembering UI state). These cookies contain no personal data and are not shared with third parties.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Our application integrates with the following third-party services:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-3">
        <li>
          <strong>Supabase</strong> — Used as our backend infrastructure for serving place data and powering the AI trip planner. Supabase processes requests on our behalf but does not receive personally identifiable information from users. Their privacy policy is available at <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" class="text-[#0066cc] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">supabase.com/privacy</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Google Maps</strong> — When you export or download a trip itinerary as a PDF, the document may include links to Google Maps for navigation purposes. Clicking these links will take you to Google Maps, which is governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-[#0066cc] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        We carefully select third-party services and only integrate with those that maintain strong privacy and security standards.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Since your data is stored locally in your browser, you have full control over its retention. You can clear your data at any time by:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li>Clearing your browser's local storage for our domain</li>
        <li>Using your browser's "Clear site data" functionality</li>
        <li>Using any in-app reset or clear options we provide</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        We do not retain any personal data on our servers. Anonymised, aggregated analytics data (if collected) may be retained for up to 12 months to help us improve the service.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:hello@exploresg.info" class="text-[#0066cc] hover:underline">hello@exploresg.info</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-[#eee] bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-[13px] text-[#999]">&copy; 2026 Explore Singapore. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-[13px] text-[#666] hover:text-[#111] transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="text-[13px] text-[#666] hover:text-[#111] transition-colors">Terms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
